==发行==
影片随《[[索女·喪屍·機關槍|索女·喪屍·機關槍]]》以《刑房系列电影》的名义在美国和加拿大影院{{le|连映|Double feature}}，在海外以加长版形式分别发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ingloriousbastards.nl/grindhouse.php |title=Alles Over Quentin Tarantino |accessdate=2007-03-30 |date=2007-03-18 |language=nl|dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071211065903/http://www.ingloriousbastards.nl/grindhouse.php |archivedate=2007-12-11  }}</ref>。加长版新增附带“缺少卷轴”标题卡提示的多个美国影院发行版未出现的片段，包括[[膝上舞|膝上舞]]镜头，总共增加27分钟的镜头。2007年8月20日，影片在[[愛丁堡國際電影節|愛丁堡國際電影節]]首映，佐伊·贝尔出席首映礼<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.variety.com/index.asp?layout=cannes2007&jump=review&reviewid=VE1117933735&cs=1&p=0 |title=Review of ''Death Proof'' |accessdate=2007-06-22 |last=McCarthy |first=Todd |date=2007-05-22 |work=Variety |archive-date=2007-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012011803/http://www.variety.com/index.asp?layout=cannes2007&jump=review&reviewid=VE1117933735&cs=1&p=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

影片的荷兰版海报以作品吸收罗伯特·罗德里格兹作品“未来概念”为卖点<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.a-film.nl/film.php?id=00002002 |title=Dutch ''Death Proof'' poster art |accessdate=2007-04-09 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070521044112/http://www.a-film.nl/film.php?id=00002002 |archivedate=2007-05-21  }}</ref>。影片于2007年9月21日在英国发行，2007年11月1日在澳大利亚发行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?nid=20659 |title=Grindhouse Dismantled |date=2007-04-30 |accessdate=2007-05-10 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927235327/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?nid=20659 |archivedate=2007-09-27  }}</ref>。塔伦蒂诺解释在海外分开发行的原因：“非英语国家没有这个传统......他们不懂刑房的真正含义，没有连映传统，所以这就要你教他们一些新东西了<ref name="RottenT">{{cite web| title=Rotten Tomatoes| work=Tarantino Chops Feature Length "Death Proof" For "Grindhouse"| url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/news/1648557/| accessdate=2007-04-18| dead-url=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070819050501/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/news/1648557/| archivedate=2007-08-19}}</ref>。”

==评价==
===专业评价===
《金刚不坏》获得总体上褒贬不一的评价，[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]评论41条，平均得分5.72/10，新鲜度63%。网站共识写道：“《金刚不坏》跟塔伦蒂诺的大制作相比可能显得微不足道，但就其自身有点来说，影片就好像打包了足量的猛料，打造辛烷值足够高的磨房产物<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_proof/ |title=Death Proof (2007) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |access-date=2019-10-10 |archive-date=2019-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522115410/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_proof/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”法国電影杂志《[[电影手册|電影筆記]]》中將影片列为2007年度十佳第二名的位置<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://alumnus.caltech.edu/~ejohnson/critics/cahiers.html#y2007 |title=Cahiers du Cinema: 2007 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305113358/http://alumnus.caltech.edu/%7Eejohnson/critics/cahiers.html#y2007 |archive-date=2012-03-05 |access-date=2018-12-01 }}</ref>。

《[[帝国杂志|帝国杂志]]》给出4/5星的正面评价，指影片如同“塔伦蒂诺受人影响开野车”，“非常有娱乐性”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.empireonline.com/reviews/ReviewComplete.asp?FID=134990 |title=Empire's Death Proof movie review |access-date=2013-02-23}}</ref>。英国广播公司的安娜·史密斯（{{lang|en|Anna Smith}}）表示，尽管影片给人带来欢乐，但受限于过时、低成本的电影制作风格，或许在这种情况下谈论这种流派的缺点未免过于苛刻。她给出了3/5星的评价<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2007/09/17/death_proof_2007_review.shtml |title=BBC Movies Death Proof review |date=2007-09-21 |access-date=2013-02-23 |archive-date=2010-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100916095941/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2007/09/17/death_proof_2007_review.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[罗杰·伊伯特|罗杰·伊伯特]]给予《刑房》系列2.5/4性，表示尽管《金刚不坏》是阵容中最令人赏心悦目的一部分，但仍然被冗长的说明性对话场景所破坏<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20071025/REVIEWS/710250304 |title=Grindhouse |last=Ebert |first=Roger |date=2007-10-26 |work=Chicago Sun-Times |access-date=2009-05-12 |archive-date=2008-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081229071755/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20071025%2FREVIEWS%2F710250304 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《卫报》的{{le|彼得·布拉德肖|Peter Bradshaw}}很欣赏追车戏，称之为“娱乐人的疯狂咆哮”，但也认为影片充斥着“充斥很长很长的诡异的对话”，或许是《落水狗》和《低俗小说》出色的即兴表演的伟大降临，总体而言，“塔伦蒂诺扭曲的才能是大家有目共睹的——不过，现在必须得承认，（这种才华）太过昙花一现了<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2007/sep/21/quentintarantino.horror |title=The Guardian's Death Proof review |last=Bradshaw |first=Peter |date=2007-09-21 |access-date=2013-02-23 |location=London |archive-date=2013-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130926081424/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2007/sep/21/quentintarantino.horror |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”塔伦蒂诺在一场导演圆桌会中表示：“《金刚不坏》是我所创作的电影中最差的一部。就左撇子电影而言，它还不算糟糕，对吧？所以如果那是我拍过的最差劲的电影，我觉得还好<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://collider.com/quentin-tarantino-death-proof-worst-film-interview/ |title=Quentin Tarantino Says DEATH PROOF Is the “Worst” Film He’s Ever Made; Watch Full Directors Roundtable Interview |last=Chitwood |first=Adam |date=2012-11-28 |website=Collider |access-date=2015-11-24 |archive-date=2015-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151205051552/http://collider.com/quentin-tarantino-death-proof-worst-film-interview/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

